    <button class="large secondary" href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1UfTWYaESVp987ebwVq4kIE4ghTeypzSB?usp=sharing" target="_blank">Download Forms</button>
  </center>
</p>

<p><strong>Working Virtually</strong><br />
This year, we are completely virtual due to COVID-19. At no time during the event will you be expected to travel anywhere physically. Due to this, you will be able to stay at home, under the supervision of your parent/guardian. The two online platforms we are using are Hopin and Discord. We may also use YouTube and Webex as a backup. If anyone not part of the organizing team (will have the Organizer role in Discord) invites you to a different platform, please contact Lina at (513) 550-3857 or on Discord at wcrklmn#1829.</p>

<p>On the Discord server, we will have text and voice channels dedicated for minors only. This is a space where only minors and organizers will be able to chat. This effort will ensure we can offer mandated supervision for all minors.</p>

